Source: xubuntu-artwork
Section: x11
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Xubuntu Developers <xubuntu-devel@lists.ubuntu.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 7.0.50~)
Standards-Version: 3.9.1
Vcs-Bzr: lp:xubuntu-artwork
Vcs-Browser: http://bazaar.launchpad.net/~xubuntu-art/xubuntu-artwork/maverick/files

Package: zevenos-artwork
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, shimmer-themes, libnewt0.52 (>= 0.52.11-2ubuntu7)
Recommends: plymouth-theme-xubuntu-logo, plymouth-theme-xubuntu-text,
 xubuntu-wallpapers, xubuntu-icon-theme
Description: ZevenOS themes and artwork
 This package contains ZevenOS themes and artwork.

Package: zevenos-wallpapers
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: ZevenOS wallpapers
 This package contains the default wallpapers for ZevenOS.

Package: plymouth-theme-zevenos-logo
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, plymouth, plymouth-label
Provides: plymouth-theme
Description: graphical boot animation and logger - zevenos-logo theme
 Plymouth is an application that runs very early in the boot process
 (even before the root filesystem is mounted!) that provides a graphical
 boot animation while the boot process happens in the background.
 .
 This package contains the default xubuntu-logo theme.

Package: plymouth-theme-zevenos-text
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, plymouth, plymouth-theme-ubuntu-text
Provides: plymouth-theme
Description: graphical boot animation and logger - zevenos-text theme
 Plymouth is an application that runs very early in the boot process
 (even before the root filesystem is mounted!) that provides a graphical
 boot animation while the boot process happens in the background.
 .
 This package contains the default xubuntu-text theme used when no support for
 a graphical theme is found on your system.

Package: zevenos-icon-theme
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: ZevenOS icon theme
 This package contains the default icon theme for ZevenOS.
